01:06:18,680 --> 01:06:20,959
You the kid with the tape?
Y-yeah.

1220
01:06:20,960 --> 01:06:23,439
Good. Come in.
I wanna try my new VCR.

1221
01:06:23,440 --> 01:06:25,359
How did you know'?
