1302
01:10:19,880 --> 01:10:21,370
Stop him!

1303
01:10:28,440 --> 01:10:30,090
Hey, kid - hop in!

1304
01:10:33,800 --> 01:10:36,359
What are you -
some kind of guardian angel?

1305
01:10:36,360 --> 01:10:38,279
Well, I guess you can say that.

1306
01:10:38,280 --> 01:10:40,039
'Cause in a manner of speaking,

1307
01:10:40,040 --> 01:10:42,519
