that we are guardians.

1308
01:10:42,520 --> 01:10:44,799
Guardians of important packages
and priority communiques.

1309
01:10:44,800 --> 01:10:47,919
(Wearily) Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Just get me home, will ya'?

1310
01:10:47,920 --> 01:10:51,159
Well, if you absolutely, positively
have to be home by tomorrow morning,

1311
01:10:51,160 --> 01:10:53,359
