(Honks horn)

1312
01:10:53,360 --> 01:10:56,119
Man, you don't let off
for a second, do ya'?

1313
01:10:56,120 --> 01:10:58,319
I have no idea what you're talking about.

1314
01:10:58,320 --> 01:11:00,999
(Mimics Joey) “I have no idea
what you're talking about.”

1315
01:11:01,000 --> 01:11:03,159
Just tell me what to do, OK'?

1316
01:11:03,160 --> 01:11:04,650
Get in.

1317
01:11:07,520 --> 01:11:10,126
Federal Express, huh? OK, thanks.

1318
01:11:11,120 --> 01:11:14,719
Oh, Al... Can I have a word with you?

1319
01:11:14,720 --> 01:11:16,529
Oh, sure, boss.

1320
01:11:17,640 --> 01:11:20,319
Remember when you told me
North was dead?

1321
01:11:20,320 --> 01:11:21,799
