1325
01:11:40,400 --> 01:11:43,519
But the stain in this cap
comes from borscht.

1326
01:11:43,520 --> 01:11:45,519
Borscht'?
Yes, borscht.

1327
01:11:45,520 --> 01:11:47,839
A beef-based soup, Russian in origin,

1328
01:11:47,840 --> 01:11:51,519
most frequently served chilled
with a dollop of sour cream.

1329
01:11:51,520 --> 01:11:55,679
I make a good borscht.
And I'd love to sample it someday.

1330
01:11:55,680 --> 01:11:57,519
The point I'm making here, Al,

1331
01:11:57,520 --> 01:11:59,959
is that unless North's head

1332
01:11:59,960 --> 01:12:03,359
