this traditional Slavic delicacy,

1333
01:12:03,360 --> 01:12:05,439
HE'S NOT DEAD, YOU IDIOT!

1334
01:12:05,440 --> 01:12:07,799
Oh, no! There's been...
Not now, Arthur.

1335
01:12:07,800 --> 01:12:11,202
Alright, alright. This just calls
