Alright.

1337
01:12:22,360 --> 01:12:24,399
Sign on the fourth line.

1338
01:12:24,400 --> 01:12:25,879
What time is it?

1339
01:12:25,880 --> 01:12:28,359
Normally, my answer would be
no later than 10:30,

1340
01:12:28,360 --> 01:12:30,799
but thanks to that jackknifed truck
on the highway,

1341
01:12:30,800 --> 01:12:33,326
I'm sorry to say it's almost 10 off 12.

1342
01:12:35,000 --> 01:12:36,999
We'll... we'll be happy
to refund your, er...

1343
01:12:37,000 --> 01:12:38,679
No, that's OK.

1344
01:12:38,680 --> 01:12:43,199
Mom! Dad! I'm home!

1345
01:12:43,200 --> 01:12:44,690
Mom!

1346
01:12:45,680 --> 01:12:48,079
Where are you guys?

1347
01:12:48,080 --> 01:12:49,730
Mom? Dad'?

1348
01:12:51,920 --> 01:12:53,410
Mom?

1349
01:12:54,560 --> 01:12:56,079
(DRAMATIC MUSIC) Mom?

1350
01:12:56,080 --> 01:12:58,079
Hello, North - happy Labor Day.

1351
01:12:58,080 --> 01:13:00,319
I trust your summer
was an enjoyable one.

1352
01:13:00,320 --> 01:13:03,519
Where are my folks?
Oh, they're in a safe place.

1353
01:13:03,520 --> 01:13:06,119
Where the hell are my parents?

1354
01:13:06,120 --> 01:13:09,039
