broadened me, you little asshole!

1359
01:13:21,480 --> 01:13:22,959
Why are you smiling?

1360
01:13:22,960 --> 01:13:24,439
I was just thinking

1361
01:13:24,440 --> 01:13:26,319
what a beautiful,
heartwarming scene it'll be

1362
01:13:26,320 --> 01:13:27,919
when you're reunited with your parents

1363
01:13:27,920 --> 01:13:29,679
at that secret spot of yours.

1364
01:13:29,680 --> 01:13:32,079
How do you know about my secret spot'?

1365
01:13:32,080 --> 01:13:35,479
I'm a journalist, North. It's my job
to know about these things.

1366
01:13:35,480 --> 01:13:37,959
And as much as I'm enjoying
this little chat,

1367
01:13:37,960 --> 01:13:39,799
shouldn't you be on your way?

1368
01:13:39,800 --> 01:13:41,404
After all, you're down to...

1369
01:13:42,480 --> 01:13:43,959
nine minutes.

1370
01:13:43,960 --> 01:13:46,964
(DRAMATIC MUSIC RESUMES)

1371
01:13:56,840 --> 01:14:00,003
