Winchell said he'd be here by now.

1372
01:14:01,040 --> 01:14:03,359
Don't worry - I'm sure he'll be here soon.

1373
01:14:03,360 --> 01:14:06,039
Soon may not be good enough!
Let me remind you.

1374
01:14:06,040 --> 01:14:09,279
