and North shows up and we miss him?

1382
01:14:45,880 --> 01:14:47,959
Relax, honey.

1383
01:14:47,960 --> 01:14:49,849
Winchell's a man of his word.

1384
01:14:59,520 --> 01:15:01,010
Ugh!

1385
01:15:05,000 --> 01:15:06,799
