1406
01:16:39,040 --> 01:16:40,519
What's that'?

1407
01:16:40,520 --> 01:16:42,759
Oh, nothin'.

1408
01:16:42,760 --> 01:16:45,519
Just something I've always had.

1409
01:16:45,520 --> 01:16:47,727
You know - for good luck.

1410
01:16:49,520 --> 01:16:50,719
Yeah, well, maybe good luck for you...

1411
01:16:50,720 --> 01:16:53,121
I bet that eagle's whistlin'
a different tune.

1412
01:16:54,120 --> 01:16:56,759
Here we go - 35 Maple Drive.

1413
01:16:56,760 --> 01:16:59,764
(SOOTHING MUSIC)

1414
01:17:06,280 --> 01:17:09,079
