Don't mention it, kid.

1415
01:17:09,080 --> 01:17:14,080
And remember - be it ever so humble,
there's no place like home.

1416
01:17:14,680 --> 01:17:18,079
With the possible exception of Vegas
when Sinatra's in town.

1417
01:17:18,080 --> 01:17:19,570
'Bye.

1418
01:17:31,640 --> 01:17:33,799
North!
North?

1419
01:17:33,800 --> 01:17:35,290
Mom! Dad!

1420
01:17:40,920 --> 01:17:43,366
Where were you?
We were worried sick!

1421
01:17:44,360 --> 01:17:47,119
I fell asleep in the mall.
Uh...

1422
01:17:47,120 --> 01:17:49,359
We called the hospitals,
we called the police...

1423
01:17:49,360 --> 01:17:51,639
Uh, we looked everywhere.

1424
01:17:51,640 --> 01:17:53,119
You did?

1425
01:17:53,120 --> 01:17:55,279
'Course we did.

1426
01:17:55,280 --> 01:17:57,681
We love you so much, North.

1427
01:17:59,000 --> 01:18:03,279
If anything ever happened to you,
I don't know what we'd do. (Kisses)

1428
01:18:03,280 --> 01:18:05,479
I love you guys too.

1429
01:18:05,480 --> 01:18:06,959
<i>C' mun .</i>

1430
01:18:06,960 --> 01:18:09,119
You hungry, honey'?
A little bit.

1431
01:18:09,120 --> 01:18:10,759
A little bit'? A little bit!

1432
01:18:10,760 --> 01:18:12,279
OK, a lot.
OK.

1433
01:18:12,280 --> 01:18:15,239
I'll tell you what - you run
upstairs, put on your pyjamas,

1434
01:18:15,240 --> 01:18:17,399
we'll bring something up
and tuck you in.

1435
01:18:17,400 --> 01:18:18,890
OK.

